==Finnish==
===Noun===

#(''neutral, decreasingly common'') a negro, a person of african descent. 
#(''varying from pejorative to humorous'') a person with significantly darker than average skin tone.
#(''usually humorous'') an imaginary "faqueer" kind of a worker. Talking about an extremely difficult job: ''Kukahan neekeri me saadaan tekemään se?'' Who's the nigger you think we will get to do it?

Originally non-pejorative, but more and more often used in a pejorative manner. Many right-wing people use this instead of [[nekru]], so to remain within somewhat acceptable terms in the public. 

The humorousness of the second case is often interpreted by the person in question, so extreme care must be observed.

